{"tid":1305483,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"張超雄加入金鐘絕食","createTime":"2019-07-11T00:55:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T05:13:47.000Z","uid":25558,"like":45,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"10ec15f6b64d900de3a0717d5465d0ac17fda154","tid":1305483,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T00:55:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190711/20725630\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190711%2F20725630&d=GTvhkYpGRy3WajvnblfJnT11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=9bb7ff88\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190711%2F20725630&h=eba3ce0c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190711/20725630</a><br />\n<br />\n張超雄加入金鐘絕食<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190711/large/a0602a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190711%2Flarge%2Fa0602a.gif&h=8496082c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n張超雄（左）昨晚宣佈即時加入金鐘絕食；右二為已絕食多日的陳伯。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】金鐘海富絕食行動昨踏入第八天，政府至今未回應絕食者的四大訴求或與他們溝通，惟絕食者強調絕不放棄，昨晚更宣佈無限期絕食，堅持不撤不散，而立法會議員張超雄亦加入絕食行列。絕食行動發言人稱，下周日起還有三名市民加入隊伍，使參加絕食的市民增至14人。<br />\n<br />\n張超雄稱擔心絕食者健康，「擔心幫佢哋唔到，不如加入埋佢哋，一來係受到佢哋道德感召，二來希望同佢哋一齊，有啲乜嘢，可以一齊支援佢哋」，加入也是對他們的支持及鼓勵。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n市民向陳伯送上寶礦力<br />\n<br />\n絕食行動發言人稱，為保障參加者健康及安全，行動將改以馬拉松接力方式進行，即是當某絕食者已到臨界點時會暫停絕食，由其他人接力；呼籲市民在各區加入絕食行動，希望能遍地開花，讓政府感受壓力，最終能回應訴求：撤回《逃犯修訂》條例、成立獨立調查委員會、撤回暴動罪、釋放及撤銷示威者控罪。 <br />\n<br />\n絕食者之一陳伯年紀老邁，有網民發起「拯救陳伯行動」，前往勸他暫停絕食，有人送上樽裝水及寶礦力。前區議員兼退休社工梁錦滔呼籲不用擔心，因醫護人員每天替他們包括陳伯量血壓及驗血糖，如醫生認為不適合絕食便會停止。<br />\n<br />\n■記者徐雲庭  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n追思女戰友「代你走下去」"},{"pid":"6547bed000a553659b8cedb9986210bca0250476","tid":1305483,"uid":38358,"like":7,"dislike":36,"score":-29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T00:59:29.000Z","msg":"食緊人血饅頭呀佢，扮乜野絕食呀"},{"pid":"04121239125d5ce37d9112f3a8109c90af4c8104","tid":1305483,"uid":189109,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T01:01:15.000Z","msg":"支持張生絕食至死嚟令政府醒覺 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有張生接力，陳伯快啲返屋企啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81ebc589176979eca3583bf3f9f98edae324537a","tid":1305483,"uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":14,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T01:38:09.000Z","msg":"張超雄快D絕死"},{"pid":"78d2f3e521764c7a0ed84d5881c3ed35e99ceb12","tid":1305483,"uid":94327,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T01:59:38.000Z","msg":"擔心陳伯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />絕食咗好多日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb0184b4d627491c1379549f3f62c928b9181d40","tid":1305483,"uid":213379,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T02:00:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DKniOCc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDKniOCc.png&h=16423938&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AmiFhvx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAmiFhvx.png&h=0870e1aa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aCMjx3T.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaCMjx3T.png&h=064f9319&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9f6e568b579a3fe1db5264a05e69bb1def8c5c6f","tid":1305483,"uid":108337,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T02:01:36.000Z","msg":"將軍唔帶兵 去絕食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04da280b09d1753766642bfc275d2d5f5ea2e189","tid":1305483,"uid":64743,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T02:01:41.000Z","msg":"絕食最冇用<img s